source.name: 2010 Small Area Health Insurance Estimates (SAHIE) Interactive Data and Mapping Tool
source.description: The Interactive Data and Mapping Tool provides users a way to access all post-2005 SAHIE data; in multiple formats; in a sleek, organized, and innovative way.  Currently, data can be downloaded as a Pdf, CSV or screenshot.
